{"tid":1660764,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"查案既入一入黎","createTime":"2019-10-17T16:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T17:07:09.000Z","uid":59868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"590fa3276d49f0de68a858958440ad0b9b0b967b","tid":1660764,"uid":59868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:42:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191018&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60161850\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191018%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60161850&d=vw1niP5YtVVR3vfDaqqaAbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=a04c39f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191018%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60161850&h=30d20af1\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191018&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60161850</a><br />\n<br />\n求下你地唔好再咁沉迷查案啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用心幫手文宣同推行動post好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我明手足們既死好多疑點<br />\n但一日唔推番個制度<br />\n一日都唔會幫到佢地伸冤<br />\n比你係福爾摩斯查到真相後<br />\n你打算自己報仇定比資料黑警？<br />\n<br />\n自己報仇=行私刑=被通緝/被捕&gt;<br />\n黑警知你知太多野&gt;變浮屍<br />\n<br />\n比資料黑警&gt;黑警知你知太多野&gt;變浮屍<br />\n<br />\n結論就係知到真相=變浮屍<br />\n<br />\n何況好多野都好難知真偽<br />\n倒不如落力推行動推文宣<br />\n再唔係宣傳和理非點樣升級做物資兵<br />\n或者宣傳打狗救人，等更多人救人<br />\n每救一個人=少一條浮屍<br />\n咁樣先係真正幫到件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等我地真係煲底除罩相擁果陣<br />\n先至再落力幫班以故手足平反啦好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b0d22ce888da2cb1f5be169d3938df3f30f9ccc","tid":1660764,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:42:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgjbDGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgjbDGh.jpg&h=e5447ac9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e6dca2a2fc808d5818e7d928f559a161e65f3713","tid":1660764,"uid":59868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:42:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc3712ab8840386145b9c5377aedcff748d17cd1","tid":1660764,"uid":183834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T17:07:09.000Z","msg":"H<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XG6qhLm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXG6qhLm.jpg&h=f4d2e9aa&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}